# Switch 开关

## 基础用法
::TuffCodeBlock{lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <script setup lang="ts">
  import { ref } from 'vue'

  const enabled = ref(true)
  </script>

  <template>
    <TuffSwitch v-model="enabled" />
  </template>
---
::

## Demo
### Toggle State
点击或使用 Enter / Space 可切换状态，位移与颜色同步变化。
:::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="SwitchToggleStateDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <script setup lang="ts">
  import { ref } from 'vue'

  const firstSwitch = ref(false)
  const secondSwitch = ref(true)
  </script>

  <template>
    <div style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;">
      <TuffSwitch v-model="firstSwitch" />
      <TuffSwitch v-model="secondSwitch" />
    </div>
  </template>
---
:::

### 不同大小
小尺寸适合密集列表，默认尺寸适合表单，大尺寸适合突出设置项。
:::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="SwitchSizesDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <script setup lang="ts">
  import { ref } from 'vue'

  const smallEnabled = ref(true)
  const defaultEnabled = ref(true)
  const largeEnabled = ref(true)
  </script>

  <template>
    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px;">
      <TuffSwitch v-model="smallEnabled" size="small" />
      <TuffSwitch v-model="defaultEnabled" />
      <TuffSwitch v-model="largeEnabled" size="large" />
    </div>
  </template>
---
:::

### 禁用效果
禁用态会降低透明度、移除聚焦，并阻止点击与键盘切换。
:::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="SwitchDisabledDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <script setup lang="ts">
  import { ref } from 'vue'

  const enabled = ref(true)
  const disabledOff = ref(false)
  const disabledOn = ref(true)
  </script>

  <template>
    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px;">
      <TuffSwitch v-model="enabled" />
      <TuffSwitch v-model="disabledOff" disabled />
      <TuffSwitch v-model="disabledOn" disabled />
    </div>
  </template>
---
:::

### 前后 Label
在开关前后放置状态文本，或与说明文案组成设置行。
:::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="SwitchLabelDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <script setup lang="ts">
  import { ref } from 'vue'

  const compact = ref(false)
  const autoSync = ref(true)
  </script>

  <template>
    <label style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
      <span>关</span>
      <TuffSwitch v-model="compact" />
      <span>开</span>
      <strong>紧凑模式</strong>
    </label>
  </template>
---
:::

### 自定义颜色
Switch 暂不提供颜色 prop，可通过 CSS 变量或局部 class 覆盖激活态颜色。
:::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="SwitchCustomColorDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <script setup lang="ts">
  import { ref } from 'vue'

  const success = ref(true)
  const warning = ref(true)
  </script>

  <template>
    <div class="custom-switch-row">
      <TuffSwitch v-model="success" class="custom-switch custom-switch--success" />
      <TuffSwitch v-model="warning" class="custom-switch custom-switch--warning" />
    </div>
  </template>

  <style scoped>
  .custom-switch-row :deep(.custom-switch--success.is-active) {
    background-color: var(--tx-color-success);
  }

  .custom-switch-row :deep(.custom-switch--warning.is-active) {
    background-color: var(--tx-color-warning);
  }
  </style>
---
:::

